# Component library (required)

**Always use existing components** from this project. Do not create new UI components, duplicate markup, or inline one-off patterns unless the user explicitly asks for a new component.

## Before building any UI

1. Check `design-reference/COMPONENTS.md` — Figma ↔ code mapping
2. Check `src/components/` and `src/components/ui/` for existing implementations
3. Compose pages from existing pieces; only add variants via `className` props

## Import paths

```tsx
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, ... } from "@/components/ui/card"
import { SiteHeader } from "@/components/SiteHeader"
import { SiteContainer } from "@/components/SiteContainer"
import { AssetTagBadge } from "@/components/portfolio/AssetTag"
import { CaseStudySection } from "@/components/portfolio/CaseStudySection"
```

## Component locations

| Folder | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `src/components/ui/` | ShadCN primitives (Button, Card, …) — add via `npx shadcn add` only when user requests |
| `src/components/` | Site shell (SiteHeader, SiteContainer, SiteLayout, PasswordGate) |
| `src/components/portfolio/` | Portfolio-specific (CaseStudySection, AssetTag, PlaceholderImage) |
| `src/pages/` | Page-level composition only — thin wrappers, no new primitives |

## When the user shares a new Figma component

1. Implement **once** in the correct folder (usually `src/components/` or `ui/`)
2. Add an entry to `design-reference/COMPONENTS.md` (name, path, props, Figma link)
3. Use that component everywhere the design appears — never copy-paste the markup

## Do NOT

- Create `NewButton.tsx` when `Button` exists
- Duplicate card markup inline when `Card` or a portfolio component fits
- Add ShadCN components without user asking
- Build parallel one-off versions of the same Figma component

## Example

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — inline duplicate
<div className="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6 shadow-elevation-1">...</div>

// ✅ GOOD — use Card or an existing portfolio component
<Card className="shadow-elevation-1">...</Card>
```

If no component exists yet, ask: "Should I add `ProjectHero` to the library from your Figma spec?" — unless the user already said to implement it.
